  "PinObjective": {
    "English": "Harvest Living Pearl from armored deep-water clams",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从装甲深海蛤蜊处收集活体珍珠",
    "TencentChinese": "从装甲深海蛤蜊处收集活体珍珠",
    "TraditionalChinese": "自裝甲深海蚌採收活珍珠"
  },
  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-commodity\">Living Pearls</span> are harvested from <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Armored Clams</span> found on the sea bed. Use the Galaxy Map to locate systems with aquatic life.<br>While swimming, identify <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Armored Clams</span> with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.<br>Increase marine efficiency by upgrading the Exosuit <span class=\"name name-technology\">Aeration Membrane</span>, refilling oxygen supplies from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Kelp Sacs</span>, or travelling in a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Nautilon Submarine</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-commodity\">活体珍珠</span>能从常见于海床上的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">装甲蛤蜊</span>中收获。使用星系图定位有水生生物的恒星系。<br>游泳时，用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>识别<span class=\"name name-stellar\">装甲蛤蜊</span>。<br>升级套装的<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝气膜</span>，从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海藻袋</span>中补充氧气补给，或搭乘<span class=\"name name-stellar\">大鹦鹉螺潜水艇</span>出行，以提高在海洋中的效率。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-commodity\">活体珍珠</span>能从常见于海床上的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">装甲蛤蜊</span>中收获。使用星系图定位有水生生物的恒星系。<br>游泳时，用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>识别<span class=\"name name-stellar\">装甲蛤蜊</span>。<br>升级套装的<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝气膜</span>，从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海藻袋</span>中补充氧气补给，或搭乘<span class=\"name name-stellar\">大鹦鹉螺潜水艇</span>出行，以提高在海洋中的效率。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-commodity\">活珍珠</span>可自海底的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">裝甲蚌</span>中採收。利用銀河系地圖尋找擁有水中生物體的星系。<br>游泳時，利用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>偵測<span class=\"name name-stellar\">裝甲蚌</span>。<br>升級強化套裝的<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝氣黏膜</span>、從<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">巨藻囊</span>補充氧氣補給，或搭乘<span class=\"name name-stellar\">巡洋龍潛艇</span>前進，以提高海洋行動的效率。"
  },
